OL,3,CMotorcyclist dies after crash
OL,4,Cinvolving HGV
OL,6,FA motorcyclist has died following a
OL,7,Fcrash in the Scottish Borders.
OL,9,FThe 44-year-old man was riding a blue
OL,10,FYamaha on the A7 north of Stow when he
OL,11,Fwas involved in a collision with a
OL,12,Fwhite Renault HGV.
OL,14,FIt happened at about 11:35am on Friday
OL,15,F21 June.
OL,17,FEmergency services attended the scene
OL,18,Fbut the motorcyclist was pronounced
OL,19,Fdead at the scene.
OL,21,FHis next of kin have been informed.
