OL,3,CMotorcyclist dies after crash
OL,4,Cinvolving HGV
OL,6,FThe driver of the HGV was uninjured.
OL,8,FSergeant Barry Sommerville said: "Our
OL,9,Fthoughts are with the family and
OL,10,Ffriends of the man who died and all
OL,11,Fthose involved and I would like to
OL,12,Fthank members of the public who
OL,13,Fstopped to assist.
OL,15,F"Enquiries are ongoing to establish
OL,16,Fthe full circumstances and we are
OL,17,Fappealing to anyone who has not
OL,18,Falready spoken to officers to get in
OL,19,Ftouch if you can assist.
